I have always been a scared person, but ever since I got to know Jesus, and I'm still in the process of getting to know Him, He has given me hope beyond I could ever understand. In Him, I can always hope for the future and be truly joyful even in sad circumstances. I hope you can get the time to know Him as well through His Word. He is the true Answer to all our broken and empty hearts. I will pray for you Sister. :)

author: @nakulmandhotra
text:
I am absolutely happy that DK covered this song  so I would further explain what the song means  , the song 'HAPPY' delves into the universal longing for pure, unadulterated happiness. The lyrics express a desire for days filled with joy, free from worries and the burdens of tomorrow. The song's narrator questions whether such days exist, where one can laugh without concerns and scream with joy upon finding their dreams. The repetition of these inquiries highlights the yearning for a state of bliss that seems just out of reach.

The song also touches on the pressures of modern life, where social media algorithms often highlight the successes of others, making one's own happiness seem elusive. The narrator's plea for help and reassurance that it's okay to be happy reflects a vulnerability and a struggle with emotional well-being. The line 'May I be happy?' is a poignant request for permission to experience joy amidst life's challenges. The song resonates with listeners who may feel overwhelmed by the complexities of daily life and the pursuit of happiness.
The song serves as a reminder that the pursuit of happiness is a common thread in the human experience, and it's okay to seek help and acknowledge the difficulty of finding joy in the midst of life's trials.

- lyricslayers

I would also suggest to check out Day6 songs they have a very great discography and lyrics which resonate with difeerent experiences and situations of life  and members with great personality

author: @parnaxbtsvt
text: This song is actually how life feels with svt...since 2023 I have been going through a lot...even it got worse since the first day of 2024...I lost so many people in my life this year...but svt came and embraced me...saved me...pulled me out from dark...I was getting lost in the dark...I don't know what my life would have been without svt now! Literally I feel like svt is a gift of god to me...once upon a time I was going through something else when other kpop bands healed me..but since last year it was the worst! And tbh no other group felt like how svt did...Svt is the happiest part of my life...I have been stanning svt since the end of 2023..but my condition was such that I couldn't focus on anything else..but finally I put my focus on svt and I am truly happy now...I will never regret stanning them..choosing them was my best decision ever....Saranghae svt...Going svt is my biggest therapy ever! The announcement of military enlistment broke my heart...but we all can wait! Caratdeul will be waiting! They have healed me so much that a 'thankyou' can't be enough...as an international carat...it will always be my dream to attend a concert... THANKYOU SVT.. â¤ I DON'T UNDERSTAND BUT I LOVE YOUğŸ’â¤ï¸â€ğŸ©¹

author: @moonbinlove
text: 'Dokyeom', could do so many childish things a lot but always hyped up about everything he does. Known as the sun flower of the group cause he makes others happy and makes their moods.His voice is so melodic and angelic that I could hear it infinitely.I have always been so happy after seventeen came into my life. I used to think even the small things so negatively but not anymore. As seventeen exist in my life, I have been told to be happy and to let go of all the negative things in my life. I never knew that someone who is so far away from me, who doesn't even know my existence could change my whole life like this. At the end of the day, when there was no one for me to share my happiness and sorrows with, seventeen showed up for me. I was able to move on from all the bad events that happened in my life thanks to you.  People like you guys are so precious in this society. You became my life line, my life saviours, my happiness and my comfort zone. I would always wish the best for all 13 of you. You all lit up the carats' world. Thank you for always making us with every little thing that you all do. In my life,I have never been so proud like this. Thank you for your hard work. I wish for a lifetime of happiness for both seventeen and carats. â¤â¤â¤â¤â¤â¤
